は思います。大臣、どう思われますか…"]}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00520220322/67", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00520220322/69", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00520220322/71", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00520220322/73", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00520220322/76", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00520220322/80", "sentence": []}]}]}, {"date": "2022-04-21", "meeting": [{"meeting_name": "参議院 総務委員会", "remarks": [{"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00820220421/113", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00820220421/115", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00820220421/117", "sentence": ["…めています。そこには、これ滋賀県の目標ですが、職員一人当たりの月平均時間外勤務時間数の数値目標として、平成二十九年度十六・六時間、十六・六時…", "…増が必要かということを自治労連が試算をしています。それによりますと、時間外勤務を減らす目標を達成するには四・二三人、年次有給休暇取得で二十五…", "…が立てた目標を達成できないという試算なんです。ただでさえ人が少なく、時間外勤務をせざるを得ず、年次休暇も目標どおりに取れないのが今の地方の自…"]}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00820220421/119", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00820220421/121", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00820220421/123", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00820220421/125", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00820220421/127", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00820220421/129", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00820220421/131", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00820220421/133", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00820220421/135", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00820220421/137", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120814601X00820220421/140", "sentence": []}]}]}]